-------------------
hrc_sib_wrap_script
-------------------
a wrap script for hrc_sib_main_script


-------------------
hrc_sib_main_script
-------------------
a contol script to run find_shield_rate.perl


---------------------
find_shield_rate.perl 
---------------------

this script extract HRC shield rate from dataseeker and plots agaisnt 
time to represent HRC SIB.

Input
/data/mta/DataSeeker/data/repository/aorbital.rdb
dataseeker:	sheild_events.dat


Output
/data/mta/www/mta_hrc/Trending/Bkg_data/shiled_rate.gif
/data/mta/www/mta_hrc/Trending/hrc_bkg.html

you need to have an access to dataseeker

